                <strong>{{custom_name}}</strong>,</p>
                <p>On this glorious <strong>Victory Day</strong>, we remember and honor the brave souls who fought for the independence of our beloved nation.</p>

                <p>May the spirit of freedom, sacrifice, and patriotism live on in our hearts. <strong>Joy Bangla! Joy Bangladesh! </strong></p>

                <p>Warm regards,<br/>
                <strong><t t-out="user.name or ''"> M Jahangir Alam</t></strong></p>
